Tinsley Grimes https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Tinsley_Grimes 0 Tinsley Grimes is an actress notable for primary, secondary, and guest starring roles in various television series.
Nina Walsh on Smart Guy (1997–99) Bobbie Wagner on Promised Land (1999) Erica on Everybody Loves Raymond (2000) Katie Howard on That 80s Show (2002) Phoebe's assistant on Charmed, Season 5: Episode "Happily Ever After" (2002) Mindy Sterngood on Tremors television series (2003) Lisa Kelly on Married to the Kellys (2003–2004) Kate on Go On (2012-2013).
